caption: Jack Finnegan Gilinsky & Jack Edward Johnson, you boys mean the absolute world to me. You've helped me through so much in my life, it's amazing. I cannot thank you guys enough, if it wasn't for you guys I don't know what I'd be doing with my life. You guys inspire me so much everyday I hear you guys sing. I just want you guys to know that no matter whether I win or lose this #contest, I still continue to love you guys infinite. ∞ continue the good work with your music, I can't wait to hear more, I love you boys. ❤️ @JackAndJackOfficial @JackGilinskyOfficial @JackJohnsonOfficial #contest #contest #contest #contest
